| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2022-2761 — Mass File Rename (alphv)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 868dd535-3e96-5cf4-8f87-21aaffaec556"
index=*
| where (file_path="*.encrypted" OR file_path="*.locked" OR file_path="*.ransom")
